[package]
name = "common_libs"
version = "1.0.0"
authors = ["Ayagasha <alexander.todorov@ayagasha.com>"]
edition = "2018"



[dependencies]
clap = {version = "2.33.4", features = ["yaml"]}
serde = { version = "1.0", features = ["derive"] }
rand = "0.8.4"
inner = "0.1.1"
serde_json = "1.0.68"
chrono = { version = "0.4", features = ["serde"] }
tokio = { version = "1", features = ["full"] }
crossbeam = "0.8.1"
futures = "0.3.17"
async-std = "1.10.0"
reqwest = {version = "0.11.7"}
rodio = "0.14.0"
scraper = "0.12.0"
itertools = "0.10.1"
ansi_term = "0.12.1"
log = { version = "0.4", features = ["max_level_info", "release_max_level_info"] }
log4rs = "1.0.0"
